/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-field-group elementor-column elementor-field-type-submit elementor-col-100 e-form__buttons\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<button class=\"elementor-button elementor-size-sm\" type=\"submit\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-content-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-text\">Send<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/button>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/form>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-260f122 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"260f122\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-f790a3b\" data-id=\"f790a3b\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-374f4bc elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"374f4bc\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">What are spiders, where do they come from, and what do they eat?<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d5d2c22 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"d5d2c22\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p style=\"margin: 0cm;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: #0e101a;\">Spiders are small eight-legged arthropods that belong to the class of Arachnida. They have a unique body structure, divided into two segments &#8211; the cephalothorax and the abdomen. Spiders have an incredible ability to weave intricate webs using their silk-producing glands, which they use for trapping prey or protecting their eggs. Spiders feed on insects and other small arthropods, such as mites and ticks.<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin: 0cm;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: #0e101a;\">The diet of spiders varies depending on the species&#8217; size and habitat; for instance, larger spiders can consume bigger prey like frogs or birds, while smaller ones may only eat tiny insects like mosquitoes. Some spider species don&#8217;t even need to eat frequently as they can survive for months without food due to their low metabolic rate. Despite being considered pests by some people due to their appearance and venomous bites in certain cases, spiders play a vital role in controlling insect populations and maintaining the ecological balance in many ecosystems globally.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-416f9f4 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"416f9f4\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">What can spiders do to you?<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-657bc1e elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"657bc1e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p style=\"margin: 0cm;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: #0e101a;\">Spiders are one of the most feared creatures on earth. Some people are scared of their eight legs, and others are afraid of their venomous bites. While not all spiders harm humans, some species can cause significant harm or even death. Venomous spiders like black widows and brown recluses should be avoided as they can cause serious health problems.<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin: 0cm;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: #0e101a;\">The symptoms caused by a spider bite vary depending on the type of spider and the amount of venom injected. Common signs include swelling, redness, itchiness, and pain around the bite area. In severe cases, people may experience muscle pain, fever, chills or difficulty breathing, which requires urgent medical attention.<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin: 0cm;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: #0e101a;\">Despite their fearsome reputation, spiders play an essential role in our ecosystem. They help control the population of insects like mosquitoes and flies, which can spread diseases to humans and animals alike; hence, it&#8217;s important to be cautious around them when necessary.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-da200bb elementor-section-full_width elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"da200bb\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;,&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-33 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-07f574d\" data-id=\"07f574d\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-33 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-f282da5\" data-id=\"f282da5\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d8ad4a5 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"d8ad4a5\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Residential Pest Control Service<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-458670d elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"458670d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Customized pest control treatments can be used to safeguard your living space against bothersome pests and ensure that they don&#8217;t become a nuisance in your home.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-46c751b elementor-align-center elementor-widget elementor-widget-global elementor-global-4670 elementor-widget-button\" data-id=\"46c751b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"button.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-button-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t<a class=\"elementor-button elementor-button-link elementor-size-lg\" href=\"https:\/\/acmepestsolutions.com\/appointment\/\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-content-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-text\">Book An Appointment<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/a>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-33 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-67886cc\" data-id=\"67886cc\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-56a9c3d elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"56a9c3d\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-8e8c7c0\" data-id=\"8e8c7c0\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-bd696cc elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"bd696cc\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">What can you do to avoid getting bitten by a spider?<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b1539f0 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"b1539f0\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Spiders are one of the most feared creatures in the world. While most spider bites are not dangerous to humans, some species can cause severe reactions and even death. The best way to avoid getting bitten by a spider is to take precautions when you&#8217;re out and about. Firstly, always be aware of your surroundings. Spiders hide in dark and damp places like basements, attics, and garages. If you need to enter these areas, wear protective clothing like long sleeves and pants or gloves. Keep your home clean and clutter-free, as spiders love living in messy environments.<\/p><p style=\"margin: 0cm;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: #0e101a;\">Secondly, know what type of spiders live in your area. If you live in an area with venomous spiders, such as black widows or brown recluses, take extra precautions, such as sealing up cracks around windows and doors or using insecticides.<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin: 0cm;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: #0e101a;\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin: 0cm;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: #0e101a;\">Lastly, seek medical attention immediately if you get bitten by a spider. Some spider bites can result in serious health complications if left untreated. Remember that prevention is always better than cure &#8211; stay vigilant at all times!<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4477d09 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"4477d09\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">How to get rid of spiders: the best ways to get rid of spiders in your home<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-16a4f9c elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"16a4f9c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Here are some of the best ways to get rid of spiders:<\/p><p><strong>Use a vacuum cleaner:<\/strong> This is one of the most common ways to get rid of spiders. Just vacuum up any spiders that you find, and you should be able to get rid of them.<\/p><p><strong>Use a broom and dustpan:<\/strong>\u00a0This is another common way to eliminate spiders. Just sweep up any spiders that you find, and you should be able to get rid of them.<\/p><p><strong>Use an insecticide:<\/strong>\u00a0If you find a lot of spiders in one area of your home, consider using an insecticide to get rid of them. Some insecticides are designed to kill spiders, so read the label before using it.<\/p><p><strong>Use a vacuum sealer:<\/strong>\u00a0If you have a lot of spiders, consider using a vacuum sealer to get rid of them. Vacuum sealers are often used to store food, but they can also be used to get rid of spiders. Just vacuum up any spiders that you find, and you should be able to get rid of them.<\/p><p><strong>Call a professional:<\/strong>\u00a0If you&#8217;re having trouble getting rid of spiders, consider calling a professional. They can help you get rid of spiders more effectively.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Spider Identification Color Size Description Color Some common colors include black, brown and gray. Size Spider size varies from 3mm to 35mm. Description Spiders have a unique anatomy which includes two main body parts: the cephalothorax (head and thorax fused together) and the abdomen. The head part contains eyes, mouthparts, and pedipalps, while the abdomen &#8230; <a title=\"Spider\" class=\"read-more\" href=\"https:\/\/acmepestsolutions.com\/spider\/\" aria-label=\"More on Spider\">Read more<\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"rank_math_lock_modified_date":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[37],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-5973","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","hentry","category-pest-libraries"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/acmepestsolutions.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/5973"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/acmepestsolutions.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/acmepestsolutions.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/acmepestsolutions.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/acmepe